  <brief_title>Comparing Two Methods to Stop Vomiting of Blood Using the Endoscope</brief_title>
  <official_title>Control of Acute Variceal Bleeding Using the Multi-shooter Band Ligator Compared to Injection Sclerotherapy.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
